CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

April 17, 2006

[Cite as 04/17/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-1854.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

1987-0327. State v. Clark.

Lucas App. No. L-84-443. This cause came on for further consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of execution scheduled for May 2, 2006,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion is denied.
